# --- Structural tier names (mastery.node.<tail>.title / .desc). The mod composes a fanned
#     node's title as "<track title>: <tier name>" via its mastery.node_title.format key, so
#     ONE key per template tier localizes every track that extends combat6_standard, custom
#     skills included. A per-node mastery.<nodeId>.title key always wins over composition.
#     The desc takes {0} = localized track title, {1} = localized target skill name. ---
