# --- Hand-authored eternal node descriptions ---
mastery.acr_eternal.desc = Each purchase: +0.5% acrobatics mastery bonus-drop chance. Cost grows 10% per purchase. Grind without limit.
mastery.enc_eternal.desc = Each purchase: +0.5% enchanting mastery bonus-drop chance. Cost grows 10% per purchase. Grind without limit.
mastery.fb_eternal.desc = Each purchase: +1% Fireball damage. Cost grows 25% per purchase. Requires MAGIC level 92.
mastery.fis_eternal.desc = Each purchase: +0.5% fishing mastery bonus-drop chance. Cost grows 10% per purchase. Grind without limit.
mastery.har_eternal.desc = Each purchase: +0.5% harvesting mastery bonus-drop chance. Cost grows 10% per purchase. Requires HARVESTING level 92.
mastery.met_eternal.desc = Each purchase: -1% Meteor cooldown and +0.75% Meteor damage. Cost grows 10% per purchase (capped after 70). Requires MAGIC level 92.
mastery.min_eternal.desc = Each purchase: +0.5% mining mastery bonus-drop chance. Cost grows 10% per purchase. Requires MINING level 92.
mastery.ps_eternal.desc = Each purchase: +1% Piercing Shot damage (swing & cast). Cost grows 10% per purchase. Requires ARCHERY level 92.
mastery.sst_eternal.desc = Each purchase: -1% Shadowstep cooldown. Cost grows 10% per purchase. Requires DAGGERS level 92.
mastery.ss_eternal.desc = Each purchase: +1% Shield Slam damage. Cost grows 10% per purchase. Requires DEFENSE level 92.
mastery.ww_eternal.desc = Each purchase: +1% Whirlwind damage (swing & cast). Cost grows 10% per purchase. Requires AXES level 92.
mastery.woo_eternal.desc = Each purchase: +0.5% woodcutting mastery bonus-drop chance. Cost grows 10% per purchase. Requires WOODCUTTING level 92.

