achievement.pack_first_mastery_milestone.desc = Reach level 15 in any skill - the first Mastery Point milestone.
achievement.pack_mastery_milestone_journeyman.title = Journeyman of the Path
achievement.pack_mastery_milestone_journeyman.desc = Reach level 60 in any skill - four Mastery Point milestones earned.
achievement.pack_mastery_hoarder_300.title = Mastery Hoarder
achievement.pack_mastery_hoarder_300.desc = Earn 300 Mastery Points across your lifetime.
achievement.pack_mastery_devotee.title = Devotee of Mastery
achievement.pack_mastery_devotee.desc = The full mastery journey: an apprentice, a journeyman, and a hoarder.
